name: LILACS (Latin American and Caribbean Center on Health Sciences Information)
description: LILACS is the comprehensive index of scientific and technical literature of Latin America and the Caribbean. ####The main objectives of this database are the bibliographic control and the dissemination of health scientific-technique literature from Latin American and Caribbean countries, absentee from the international databases. It covers the description and indexing of theses, books, books chapters, congresses or conferences annals, scientific-technical reports, journal articles, etc, related to health area.
